nars.term.match

Class EllipsisMatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • nars.term.TermVector<Term>
      • nars.term.match.EllipsisMatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, java.lang.Iterable<Term>, Term, TermContainer<Term>, Termed, Termlike

    public final class EllipsisMatch
extends TermVector<Term>
implements Term
    Holds results of an ellipsis match and implements a pre-filter before forming the subterm collection, and post-filter before forming a resulting substituted term.
